title: ETF Drilldown: FRDM
description: ETFs focused on emerging-market assets saw a 17th consecutive week of inflows, with investors positioning for potential rate cuts across the developing world while the US dollar weakens. Life and Liberty Indexes Founder Perth Tolle joins "ETF IQ" to discuss. (Source: Bloomberg)
